Package dmv.spring.demo.model.repository.jdbc

JDBC implementors of Persistence layer interfaces

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CredentialsRepositoryJDBC
    JDBC implementation of CredentialsRepository interface.
    JdbcConnector
    Custom made manager for Connection and PreparedStatement, to be used in Repository classes.
    Mappers
    This Mappers are for ResultSet fields to corresponding Entity fields mapping
    RoleRepositoryJDBC
    Querying table ROLE via JDBC according to RoleRepository specification.
    UserRepositoryJDBC
    This Repository implementation will use multi-statement SQL queries that in turn may call Stored Procedures in order to create, update and get back several results within a single connection.
